<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380608' id='t-380608'>So let's start again. Let's design a product,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384297' id='t-384297'>right from the word go, and decide what we want.</span>
