<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462224' id='t-462224'>Now there are two features of mosquito biology</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465869' id='t-465869'>that really help us in this project,</span>
